These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, potato, spinach, mango
1. the person eating pineapple is on the far left##1
2. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
3. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | pineapple | potato | spinach | mango |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, juice, milk
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | lemonade | hot-chocolate | milk | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, woodworking, writing, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | reading | writing | woodworking | puzzles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, romance, epic, drama
1. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | satire | drama | epic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
