.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, trance, disco, funk
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
4. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | disco | trance | soul | funk |

 